1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:11,537
=Detik Aku Bertemu Kamu=

2
00:00:11,537 --> 00:00:14,962
=Episod 5=

3
00:00:15,912 --> 00:00:16,471
(Kementerian Kehakiman, Biro Pintu)
Pesuruhjaya.

4
00:00:17,079 --> 00:00:18,719
Laporan autopsi Li Wan dah siap?

5
00:00:23,800 --> 00:00:25,399
Pukulan tapak tangan itu
kemas dan tegas.

6
00:00:25,640 --> 00:00:26,719
Satu pukulan maut.

7
00:00:30,359 --> 00:00:31,120
Nampaknya

8
00:00:33,200 --> 00:00:34,799
Chu Yunchang tahu ilmu bela diri.

9
00:00:35,280 --> 00:00:37,399
Aku juga syak Li Wan

10
00:00:37,560 --> 00:00:39,799
takkan culik penjual bunga
tanpa sebab.

11
00:00:41,560 --> 00:00:43,719
Setiap kejadian besar di Kota

12
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:46,280
ada kaitan dengan Mahaguru
Perikatan Persilatan.

13
00:00:46,719 --> 00:00:49,960
Nampaknya kita takkan dapat jawapan
hingga Ratu Pencuri Selatan

14
00:00:50,237 --> 00:00:51,477
akhirnya muncul.

15
00:00:52,840 --> 00:00:53,880
Ketua Sekte!

16
00:00:53,880 --> 00:00:54,719
Kenapa tergesa-gesa?

17
00:00:55,280 --> 00:00:56,439
Dia sedang tukar balutan!

18
00:00:56,439 --> 00:00:57,000
Cakap!

19
00:00:57,190 --> 00:00:59,000
Wanita Seribu Tangan
sedang memaksa masuk.

20
00:00:59,050 --> 00:01:00,679
Dua Pengawal minta anda hadir.

21
00:01:18,719 --> 00:01:20,719
Jadi, kau Tupai Jed itu.

22
00:01:21,000 --> 00:01:22,239
Apa kau buat di sini?

23
00:01:23,400 --> 00:01:25,079
Aku datang nak buat cabaran.

24
00:01:25,400 --> 00:01:26,400
Cabaran?

25
00:01:27,239 --> 00:01:28,879
Aku nak bertarung.

26
00:01:29,280 --> 00:01:30,319
Pemenang

27
00:01:30,879 --> 00:01:32,959
akan jadi Mahaguru sebenar
Perikatan Persilatan.

28
00:01:37,719 --> 00:01:38,519
Baik, kau menang.

29
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:42,560
Kau...

30
00:01:42,879 --> 00:01:45,159
Aku memang cari alasan
nak lepaskan gelaran itu.

31
00:01:45,439 --> 00:01:46,400
Kalau kau nak,

32
00:01:46,480 --> 00:01:47,599
aku serahkan sekarang.

33
00:01:47,760 --> 00:01:48,480
Selamat tinggal.

34
00:01:49,079 --> 00:01:49,799
Chu Yunchang!

35
00:01:50,480 --> 00:01:51,959
Kau terlalu angkuh!

36
00:01:52,719 --> 00:01:54,319
Kau langsung tak munasabah?

37
00:01:54,560 --> 00:01:56,120
Kau datang nak buat cabaran,

38
00:01:56,400 --> 00:01:58,519
aku mengalah, kau pula hilang sabar?

39
00:01:59,799 --> 00:02:01,439
Kau tak beri aku pilihan.

40
00:02:03,000 --> 00:02:04,200
Apa kata kau tengok

41
00:02:04,599 --> 00:02:05,840
(Token Perikatan Persilatan Utara)
apa benda ini?

42
00:02:06,300 --> 00:02:09,375
(Token)

43
00:02:10,159 --> 00:02:11,000
Token Suci!

44
00:02:14,487 --> 00:02:15,587
(Token Perikatan Persilatan Utara)

45
00:02:20,520 --> 00:02:21,599
Kau bukan orang pertama

46
00:02:21,599 --> 00:02:23,080
yang mengacah Token Suci palsu.

47
00:02:23,439 --> 00:02:24,879
Kau rasa ini palsu?

48
00:02:25,360 --> 00:02:28,479
Kalau begitu, aku tinggalkan ini
di Vila Daun Merah tiga hari.

49
00:02:28,719 --> 00:02:30,240
Kalau kau tak datang ambil,

50
00:02:30,240 --> 00:02:32,000
aku serahkan pada Biro Pintu.

51
00:02:32,199 --> 00:02:35,360
Bila harta paling berharga
Sekte Tangan Suci

52
00:02:35,479 --> 00:02:37,479
jatuh ke tangan Biro,

53
00:02:37,719 --> 00:02:40,120
kau akan jadi bahan ketawa
dunia persilatan.

54
00:02:40,919 --> 00:02:42,680
Aku nak tengok
macam mana kau nak tunjuk muka

55
00:02:43,319 --> 00:02:45,080
sebagai Mahaguru
Perikatan ini nanti.

56
00:02:50,280 --> 00:02:50,960
Chang!

57
00:02:51,280 --> 00:02:53,120
Aku rasa token
dalam gambar itu memang asli.

58
00:02:53,639 --> 00:02:55,230
Kalau dia betul-betul ada Token Suci asli,

59
00:02:55,439 --> 00:02:56,879
dia dah menguasai seluruh dunia.

60
00:02:58,599 --> 00:02:59,240
Chang!

61
00:03:00,319 --> 00:03:01,190
Cepat, panggil tabib!

62
00:03:01,750 --> 00:03:02,310
Chang!

63
00:03:02,560 --> 00:03:03,240
Tak.

64
00:03:05,039 --> 00:03:06,680
Lin Xin'er masih mencurigakan.

65
00:03:07,520 --> 00:03:09,360
Orangnya pasti
mengawasi pintu masuk.

66
00:03:09,900 --> 00:03:11,240
Aku cuma perlu baring sekejap.

67
00:03:15,500 --> 00:03:17,190
(Petunjuk baru tentang Token Suci
telah terbongkar.)

68
00:03:17,719 --> 00:03:18,800
(Mahaguru masih dalam pemulihan.)

69
00:03:20,319 --> 00:03:22,520
(Aku akan tinjau Vila Daun Merah dulu.)

70
00:03:28,700 --> 00:03:30,250
(Token)

71
00:03:30,520 --> 00:03:32,080
(Token Suci memang ada di sini.)

72
00:03:34,412 --> 00:03:35,562
(Token)

73
00:03:54,879 --> 00:03:55,479
Pergi.

74
00:03:56,879 --> 00:03:57,560
Jom bergerak.

75
00:04:12,080 --> 00:04:13,700
Di mana penawar untuk
Racun Tujuh Bunga?

76
00:04:15,919 --> 00:04:18,040
Sebab kau tolak cabaran aku,

77
00:04:18,399 --> 00:04:20,279
aku terpaksa paksa kau bertindak.

78
00:04:21,079 --> 00:04:21,720
Oh ya,

79
00:04:22,920 --> 00:04:24,079
di mana Chu Yunchang?

80
00:04:24,079 --> 00:04:25,160
Kenapa dia tak keluar?

81
00:04:25,600 --> 00:04:26,399
Dia takut ke?

82
00:04:27,279 --> 00:04:28,160
Nak lawan kau,

83
00:04:28,759 --> 00:04:30,160
tak perlu Grandmaster pun.

84
00:04:30,600 --> 00:04:31,519
Aku dah cukup.

85
00:04:33,079 --> 00:04:34,079
Serahkan penawar itu.

86
00:04:35,160 --> 00:04:36,480
Aku dah letak penawar itu

87
00:04:36,480 --> 00:04:38,399
dalam Treasure Trove Putera Duan.

88
00:04:39,312 --> 00:04:40,112
Pilih tempat lain.

89
00:04:40,487 --> 00:04:41,286
Aku akan bertarung dengan kau.

90
00:04:41,519 --> 00:04:43,160
Aku cuma bertarung dengan Chu Yunchang.

91
00:04:45,079 --> 00:04:48,040
Kata pada dia, kalau nak
selamatkan nyawa Chu Xiangling,

92
00:04:48,279 --> 00:04:50,519
dia mesti dapatkan penawar sebelum aku,

93
00:04:50,639 --> 00:04:52,480
sebelum matahari terbit esok.

94
00:04:53,160 --> 00:04:53,959
Kalau tidak...

95
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:58,480
Chu Xiangling pasti mati.

96
00:05:00,912 --> 00:05:03,637
(Kediaman Chu)

97
00:05:05,519 --> 00:05:06,279
Sanbao?

98
00:05:06,920 --> 00:05:07,519
Nyonya.

99
00:05:07,759 --> 00:05:09,720
Pergi sampaikan pesan pada Gate Bureau.

100
00:05:10,360 --> 00:05:13,240
Beritahu mereka Jade Squirrel

101
00:05:13,560 --> 00:05:15,680
akan menyerbu
Kediaman Putera Duan malam ini.

102
00:05:16,399 --> 00:05:17,040
Faham.

103
00:05:18,360 --> 00:05:19,040
Rong.

104
00:05:19,279 --> 00:05:20,160
Pengintip kita lapor

105
00:05:20,600 --> 00:05:22,199
Jade Squirrel akan menyerbu

106
00:05:22,519 --> 00:05:23,839
Kediaman Putera Duan malam ini.

107
00:05:23,839 --> 00:05:25,270
Ibu kota akan jadi huru-hara.

108
00:05:25,720 --> 00:05:27,040
Bukankah kau asyik kata

109
00:05:27,040 --> 00:05:28,519
kau rasa bersalah pada Cik Chu?

110
00:05:28,920 --> 00:05:31,360
Inilah peluang terbaik untuk balas budi.

111
00:05:31,720 --> 00:05:32,399
Maksud kau...

112
00:05:33,600 --> 00:05:35,519
Cik Chu cuma seorang wanita muda,

113
00:05:35,720 --> 00:05:36,959
dan dia masih cedera.

114
00:05:37,110 --> 00:05:39,260
Tak selamat untuk dia
jaga kedai bunga itu seorang diri.

115
00:05:39,519 --> 00:05:41,759
Apa kata kau cepat pergi sana

116
00:05:41,759 --> 00:05:43,199
dan temankan dia sepanjang malam?

117
00:05:43,300 --> 00:05:44,639
Anggap saja lunaskan hutang budi.

118
00:05:45,212 --> 00:05:45,892
Wushuang,

119
00:05:45,892 --> 00:05:47,332
terima kasih sebab beritahu aku.

120
00:05:47,375 --> 00:05:48,174
Aku akan tukar baju

121
00:05:48,174 --> 00:05:48,854
dan terus ke sana.

122
00:05:48,854 --> 00:05:49,414
Bagus.

123
00:05:52,737 --> 00:05:55,857
(Malam ini, aku pasti
tangkap Jade Squirrel.)

124
00:05:59,040 --> 00:05:59,639
Cik,

125
00:05:59,920 --> 00:06:01,519
adik Mao Buyu datang jumpa cik.

126
00:06:02,720 --> 00:06:04,600
Rong? Kenapa kau datang?

127
00:06:04,720 --> 00:06:05,439
Jangan bergerak.

128
00:06:06,759 --> 00:06:08,160
Yunchang, aku minta maaf.

129
00:06:08,390 --> 00:06:09,560
Kau cedera sebab aku.

130
00:06:09,560 --> 00:06:10,790
Memang patut aku datang melawat kau.

131
00:06:10,800 --> 00:06:11,680
Kau rasa macam mana?

132
00:06:12,920 --> 00:06:13,680
Aku dah okey sekarang.

133
00:06:14,000 --> 00:06:14,879
Baguslah.

134
00:06:15,360 --> 00:06:16,680
Ini ubat parut yang terbaik.

135
00:06:16,680 --> 00:06:18,560
Harap ia bantu pemulihan kau.

136
00:06:18,920 --> 00:06:19,800
Terima kasih.

137
00:06:21,120 --> 00:06:23,480
(Adakah Mao Wenrong ada helah?)

138
00:06:23,820 --> 00:06:25,560
(Jangan sampai dia beritahu Chang
tentang rancangan)

139
00:06:25,560 --> 00:06:26,800
(di Kediaman Putera Duan.)

140
00:06:27,360 --> 00:06:28,480
Kau dah tengok dia.

141
00:06:28,720 --> 00:06:29,800
Jelas dia baik-baik saja.

142
00:06:30,120 --> 00:06:30,920
Kau boleh pergi sekarang.

143
00:06:35,120 --> 00:06:35,839
Aku tak tergesa-gesa.

144
00:06:36,120 --> 00:06:37,800
Aku nak tinggal di sini dengan kau malam ini.

145
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:39,560
Kenapa?

146
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:40,600
Tak boleh!

147
00:06:42,000 --> 00:06:42,720
Zhizhi.

148
00:06:43,360 --> 00:06:44,439
Apa masalah kau?

149
00:06:44,720 --> 00:06:46,480
Kau pelik sejak tadi.

150
00:06:47,920 --> 00:06:49,360
Dia mesti dah dengar

151
00:06:49,360 --> 00:06:51,500
apa yang berlaku
di Kediaman Putera Duan malam ini.

152
00:06:53,240 --> 00:06:54,480
Apa salahnya?

153
00:06:54,680 --> 00:06:56,000
Dah lewat.

154
00:06:56,199 --> 00:06:58,000
Kita patut tidur awal,
kau rasa?

155
00:07:00,920 --> 00:07:01,680
Rong,

156
00:07:01,920 --> 00:07:03,800
ada apa-apa jadi di kediaman itu?

157
00:07:03,800 --> 00:07:05,990
Jade Squirrel buat pertaruhan
dengan Lady Thousand-Hands.

158
00:07:06,040 --> 00:07:08,320
Dia kata dia akan menyerbu
Kediaman Putera Duan malam ini.

159
00:07:08,480 --> 00:07:10,160
Seluruh bandar kini di bawah perintah berkurung.

160
00:07:10,160 --> 00:07:11,360
Itu urusan mereka.

161
00:07:11,380 --> 00:07:12,920
Apa kena-mengena dengan kakak aku?

162
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:14,480
Dia sekarang terlantar sebab cedera

163
00:07:14,480 --> 00:07:15,560
dan perlukan rehat.

164
00:07:15,560 --> 00:07:16,800
Kau tak patut ganggu dia.

165
00:07:17,070 --> 00:07:18,120
Buyu sedang jalankan misi.

166
00:07:18,120 --> 00:07:19,120
Dia risaukan keselamatan kau.

167
00:07:19,120 --> 00:07:20,920
Jadi, aku akan tinggal di sini malam ini

168
00:07:20,920 --> 00:07:21,920
untuk lindungi kau.

169
00:07:21,920 --> 00:07:22,879
Aku takkan ke mana-mana.

170
00:07:26,680 --> 00:07:27,560
Begini,

171
00:07:27,720 --> 00:07:30,519
aku memang tak suka
diperhati masa tidur.

172
00:07:30,775 --> 00:07:31,456
Mungkin

173
00:07:32,360 --> 00:07:35,160
kau patut balik.

174
00:07:35,480 --> 00:07:37,120
Betul. Kau patut pergi.

175
00:07:37,120 --> 00:07:38,560
Biar kakak aku rehat.

176
00:07:39,560 --> 00:07:41,000
Aku cuma berjaga betul-betul di sebelah kau.

177
00:07:41,000 --> 00:07:42,040
Aku takkan buat bising.

178
00:07:42,537 --> 00:07:43,897
Keselamatan kau dipertaruhkan, Yunchang.

179
00:07:43,987 --> 00:07:45,266
Tolong, jangan menolak.

180
00:07:51,150 --> 00:07:53,470
Aku penat sikit
sebab gubah bunga tadi.

181
00:07:54,787 --> 00:07:56,148
Aku nak tidur sekejap.

182
00:07:57,120 --> 00:07:57,920
Zhizhi.

183
00:07:58,040 --> 00:07:59,920
Nyalakan colok untuk aku.

184
00:07:59,920 --> 00:08:02,319
Aku nak tidur dengan tenang.

185
00:08:05,560 --> 00:08:06,160
Baik.

186
00:08:39,925 --> 00:08:41,875
(Kediaman Putera Duan)

187
00:08:52,480 --> 00:08:53,840
(Kediaman Putera Duan)
Kita kepung tempat ini dan tunggu

188
00:08:53,840 --> 00:08:54,600
sasaran.

189
00:08:55,080 --> 00:08:56,240
Jangan beri mereka sedar.

190
00:08:56,919 --> 00:08:57,600
Yue,

191
00:08:57,600 --> 00:08:59,759
kali ini susah
nak buat tanpa orang sedar.

192
00:09:00,600 --> 00:09:01,679
Semua, bersedia!

193
00:09:02,159 --> 00:09:04,320
Tunjukkan kehebatan
Pengawal Bersulam!

194
00:09:08,759 --> 00:09:09,960
(Pengawal Bersulam, Pegawai Zhuang)
Pegawai Zhuang, ya?

195
00:09:13,399 --> 00:09:14,440
Tengok siapa ada di sini.

196
00:09:14,759 --> 00:09:16,120
Gate Bureau sedang buru pencuri.

197
00:09:16,559 --> 00:09:18,080
Kenapa Pengawal Bersulam pun ada?

198
00:09:18,440 --> 00:09:21,120
Duli Yang Teramat Mulia Putera Duan
bimbang kamu tak mampu uruskan.

199
00:09:21,440 --> 00:09:23,440
Baginda kirim pesan kepada panglima kami,

200
00:09:23,519 --> 00:09:25,660
minta Pengawal Bersulam
pimpin operasi ini.

201
00:09:25,679 --> 00:09:26,679
Sekarang kami dah tiba,

202
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:28,799
kamu boleh berundur.

203
00:09:28,799 --> 00:09:29,440
Jangan cepat sangat.

204
00:09:30,120 --> 00:09:30,799
Menangkap pencuri

205
00:09:30,799 --> 00:09:32,559
di bawah bidang kuasa Gate Bureau sahaja.

206
00:09:32,919 --> 00:09:34,799
Kepung rumah besar ini
dengan begitu menonjol,

207
00:09:34,799 --> 00:09:35,960
kau cuma buat sasaran sedar, bukan?

208
00:09:35,960 --> 00:09:37,279
Pencuri itu akan bersedia.

209
00:09:40,100 --> 00:09:42,100
Aku nak mereka tahu
siapa lawan mereka..

210
00:09:42,720 --> 00:09:45,320
Pengawal Bersulam
akan berkawal di sini malam ini.

211
00:09:45,720 --> 00:09:48,000
Kalau pencuri itu memang nak mati,

212
00:09:49,240 --> 00:09:50,799
biar mereka cuba nasib.

213
00:09:55,600 --> 00:09:56,480
Timbalan Pesuruhjaya.

214
00:09:57,020 --> 00:09:58,960
Duli Tuanku menitah
awak pimpin skuad masuk.

215
00:09:59,000 --> 00:10:00,840
untuk kawal kamar
Putera dan Permaisuri.

216
00:10:00,840 --> 00:10:01,720
Bagaimana pula arahan kami?

217
00:10:02,039 --> 00:10:05,039
Ketua Konstabel Yue,
pimpin pasukan ke Treasure Trove.

218
00:10:05,039 --> 00:10:07,080
Dengan Pengawal Bersulam di sini,

219
00:10:07,080 --> 00:10:09,840
tiada sebab bergantung
pada Biro Pintu.

220
00:10:09,879 --> 00:10:10,879
Mereka hanya menyusahkan.

221
00:10:11,240 --> 00:10:11,840
Gerak.

222
00:10:13,080 --> 00:10:13,720
Silakan ikut sini.

223
00:10:14,387 --> 00:10:16,912
(Treasure Trove)

224
00:10:19,639 --> 00:10:20,320
Siapa di situ?

225
00:10:21,480 --> 00:10:22,279
Berundur.

226
00:10:22,720 --> 00:10:23,799
Aku.

227
00:10:25,000 --> 00:10:26,660
- Sembah patik, Duli Tuanku.
- Sembah patik, Duli Tuanku.

228
00:10:27,360 --> 00:10:28,000
Duli Tuanku,

229
00:10:28,320 --> 00:10:29,279
bukankah Tuanku patut

230
00:10:29,279 --> 00:10:30,240
berada di bilik selamat?

231
00:10:30,450 --> 00:10:31,175
(Putera Duan)

232
00:10:31,200 --> 00:10:33,641
Sebab Treasure Trove ini
membebankan fikiran beta.

233
00:10:33,960 --> 00:10:35,360
Ini anugerah istana.

234
00:10:35,559 --> 00:10:37,039
Beta takkan biar calar walau sedikit.

235
00:10:37,360 --> 00:10:39,919
Beta perlu periksa inventori sendiri.

236
00:10:40,120 --> 00:10:40,679
Tapi si pencuri

237
00:10:40,679 --> 00:10:42,360
menyasarkan kamar ini.

238
00:10:42,720 --> 00:10:43,799
Memeriksanya sekarang

239
00:10:43,799 --> 00:10:44,799
nampak terlalu berisiko.

240
00:10:45,919 --> 00:10:47,360
Berisiko dari segi apa?

241
00:10:49,787 --> 00:10:51,125
(Treasure Trove)

242
00:10:51,159 --> 00:10:51,879
Duli Tuanku.

243
00:10:53,440 --> 00:10:54,720
Ini Kediaman Putera Duan.

244
00:10:54,919 --> 00:10:55,799
Rumah Putera sendiri.

245
00:10:55,799 --> 00:10:57,080
Jika Duli Tuanku mahu memeriksa

246
00:10:57,080 --> 00:10:58,360
harta Tuanku sendiri,

247
00:10:58,440 --> 00:10:59,440
apa salahnya?

248
00:11:00,170 --> 00:11:02,080
Biro Pintu ini memang kuat berlagak.

249
00:11:02,080 --> 00:11:03,559
Dan berani betul mulut kamu!

250
00:11:03,639 --> 00:11:04,879
Berani kamu arahkan Duli Tuanku?

251
00:11:04,879 --> 00:11:06,360
Bukan itu maksud kami.

252
00:11:06,360 --> 00:11:07,559
Kami cuma bimbang keselamatan bocor.

253
00:11:07,559 --> 00:11:08,519
Bocor apa?

254
00:11:08,520 --> 00:11:10,159
Putera cuma memeriksa milik baginda.

255
00:11:10,159 --> 00:11:11,080
Di mana bocornya di situ?

256
00:11:11,080 --> 00:11:12,790
Kalau pencuri ambil kesempatan
ketika ini,

257
00:11:12,919 --> 00:11:14,360
mampukah kamu tanggung akibatnya?

258
00:11:14,360 --> 00:11:15,559
Maksud kamu

259
00:11:15,559 --> 00:11:17,559
kami tak cekap?

260
00:11:18,159 --> 00:11:18,720
Kamu...

261
00:11:23,600 --> 00:11:24,639
Silakan dulu, Duli Tuanku.

262
00:11:26,000 --> 00:11:27,159
Bodoh tak berguna.

263
00:11:33,200 --> 00:11:34,080
Sebelah sini, Duli Tuanku.

264
00:11:43,919 --> 00:11:44,559
Siapa di situ?

265
00:11:45,787 --> 00:11:48,012
(Permaisuri Duan)

266
00:11:49,639 --> 00:11:50,559
Duli Tuanku?

267
00:11:50,919 --> 00:11:51,919
Apa Tuanku buat di sini?

268
00:11:52,200 --> 00:11:54,000
Beta sedang periksa
harta untuk Putera.

269
00:11:54,639 --> 00:11:55,799
Tunggu. Ada sesiapa nampak

270
00:11:55,799 --> 00:11:57,300
Permaisuri masuk Treasure Trove?

271
00:11:57,919 --> 00:11:59,039
Kami berkawal di pintu masuk.

272
00:11:59,039 --> 00:12:00,080
Tak ada sesiapa keluar masuk.

273
00:12:02,360 --> 00:12:03,360
Sebenarnya siapa kamu?

274
00:12:03,710 --> 00:12:04,919
Apa maksud semua ini?

275
00:12:04,919 --> 00:12:06,000
Beta Permaisuri Duan!

276
00:12:06,000 --> 00:12:06,919
Penyamar!

277
00:12:09,080 --> 00:12:10,000
Siapa kamu?

278
00:12:13,225 --> 00:12:16,500
♪Dendam dan sesal
bagai arak yang kuat♪

279
00:12:16,538 --> 00:12:19,413
♪Teguk saja, lalu lepaskan♪

280
00:12:19,913 --> 00:12:25,631
♪Cawan kosong untuk cinta dan benci♪

281
00:12:26,813 --> 00:12:30,133
♪Air mata kaburkan takdir di luar kawalan♪

282
00:12:30,537 --> 00:12:33,457
♪Mari minum sampai fajar♪

283
00:12:34,025 --> 00:12:39,265
♪Di sebalik topeng ini, aku takkan berdusta♪

284
00:12:40,813 --> 00:12:43,206
♪Setiap pertemuan semula terasa seperti pertama♪

285
00:12:43,206 --> 00:12:46,856
♪Senyum tersembunyi ini takkan pudar♪

286
00:12:46,925 --> 00:12:50,415
♪Satu hati, tetap di sisimu♪

287
00:12:50,513 --> 00:12:53,488
♪Hingga ke hujung waktu♪

288
00:12:53,488 --> 00:12:56,863
♪Bulan melakar wajahmu♪

289
00:12:57,050 --> 00:13:00,638
♪Diselimuti awan, kau penuhi hatiku♪

290
00:13:00,638 --> 00:13:06,878
♪Mencarimu
dan pegang janji kita selamanya♪

291
00:13:07,213 --> 00:13:10,428
♪Doa yang sunyi dalam jiwaku♪

292
00:13:10,713 --> 00:13:14,251
♪Membawa sumpahku di bawah bulan♪

293
00:13:14,538 --> 00:13:17,563
♪Semoga kita tak terpisah lagi♪

294
00:13:17,563 --> 00:13:20,663
♪Dalam perjalanan menuju selamanya♪

295
00:13:20,663 --> 00:13:24,513
♪Bulan melakar wajahmu♪

296
00:13:24,513 --> 00:13:27,873
♪Diselimuti awan, kau penuhi hatiku♪

297
00:13:28,063 --> 00:13:34,023
♪Mencarimu
dan pegang janji kita selamanya♪

298
00:13:35,100 --> 00:13:44,740
♪Hanya untuk bersamamu♪

